{
  "abstract": "As a smallholder farmer in Zambia’s Eastern\r\nProvince, Lungu’s biggest source of cash to turn\r\nhis dreams into reality will come from the sale of\r\ngroundnuts. And for the last two seasons, the\r\nmarkets have been paying Lungu well for the\r\nnew high-yielding variety of groundnuts he is\r\nnow growing. MGV-4, also known as CG-7, was\r\nrecently released in Zambia and the red-colored\r\ngroundnut has higher yields than the other\r\nvarieties Lungu previously grew. Today Lungu is\r\nno longer just a dreamer. Tangible rewards from\r\nthe marketplace have turned his dreams into the\r\nfi rst steps of a new reality.",
